Problem Statement :
If n = 6, print
     #
    ##
   ###
  ####
 #####
######

Problem Statement Link :
https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/staircase/problem?isFullScreen=true

Solution :
void staircase(int n)
{
    for(int i = 0; i < n; i++,cout<<endl)
    {
        for(int j = n - 1; j > i; j--)
            cout<<" ";
        for(int j = 0; j <= i; j++)
            cout<<"#"; 
    }
}
